lisp_spec:
(task
  (name "findSecret")
  (signature ((text str)) str)
  (constraints
    (constraint "The input text will contain a single line at the end that starts with 'The secret word you are looking for is: ' followed by the secret word.")
  )
  (goal
    (description "Extract and return the secret word mentioned at the very end of the provided text.")
    (rule "Identify the line in the text that contains the phrase 'The secret word you are looking for is: '.")
    (rule "Extract the word immediately following this phrase.")
    (return "Return only the secret word as a string. If the phrase is not found, return an empty string.")
  )
)
